# =============================================
# USER SERVICE API TESTS
# Base URL: http://localhost:8080 (qua Gateway)
# =============================================

### 1. Lấy danh sách tất cả Users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Accept: application/json

### 2. Lấy thông tin 1 User theo UUID (thay ID thật vào)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Đăng ký tài khoản mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_player_01",
  "email": "testplayer01@chess.com",
  "password": "Test@12345",
  "fullName": "Test Player One"
}

### 4. Đăng nhập
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testplayer01@chess.com",
  "password": "Test@12345"
}
